================================================================================
  E-COMMERCE BACKEND — COMPLETE AUDIT: PROFESSIONALISM, PRODUCTION & PERFORMANCE
================================================================================

This document lists every issue found across the project that would cause problems
in a production environment or look unprofessional in a large-scale project.

================================================================================
  CRITICAL (HIGH PRIORITY) — Can crash or cause data loss in production
================================================================================

1. 

2.  ❌ NO STOCK DEDUCTION ON ORDER
    Files: Modules/Order/Services/OrderService.php
    Issue: No code deducts inventory stock when an order is placed. Inventory
           stock table is never updated after order creation.
    Fix:   Implement stock deduction in OrderService after order is confirmed.

3.  ❌ NO ORDER STATUS WORKFLOW VALIDATION
    Files: Modules/Order/app/Models/Order.php
    Issue: No status transition validation. An order can go from "pending" to
           "cancelled" back to "completed" with no checks.
    Fix:   Add a status workflow matrix to prevent invalid transitions.

4.  ❌ NO TRANSACTION ON PAYMENT + ORDER CREATION
    Files: Modules/Order/Services/OrderService.php
    Issue: Order creation and payment creation may not be wrapped in a single
           DB transaction. If payment succeeds but order fails, data is orphaned.
    Fix:   Wrap order+payment creation in DB::transaction().

5.  ❌ PRODUCT VARIANT SKU UNIQUE VALIDATION ON UPDATE
    File: Modules/Catalog/app/Http/Requests/UpdateProductRequest.php (line 42)
    Issue: Same as #1 — "variants.*.sku" uses "required_with:variants|string|max:100"
           with no unique check at all. You could save duplicate SKUs.
    Fix:   Add proper unique validation with ignore.

6.  ❌ LACK OF RATE LIMITING ON API ROUTES
    Files: Modules/*/routes/api.php
    Issue: Public API routes (if any) lack throttle middleware. Could be abused.
    Fix:   Apply 'throttle:60,1' middleware to public API routes.

7.  ❌ MISSING XSS PROTECTION IN SEVERAL VIEWS
    Files: Multiple Blade templates use {{ }} but some use {!! !!} rendering
    Issue: Unescaped output in several places (e.g. product descriptions).
    Fix:   Review all {!! !!} usages and only allow on trusted HTML.

8.  ❌ NO QUERY CACHING FOR FREQUENT QUERIES
    Files: Multiple services (BrandService, CategoryService, etc.)
    Issue: getBrands(), getCategories() etc. run on every page load.
           100 users × 10 pages = 1000 unnecessary DB queries per minute.
    Fix:   Cache results for 5-10 minutes using Cache::remember().

9.  ❌ MISSING IMAGE VALIDATION & SIZE CHECK
    File: Modules/Catalog/app/Http/Requests/StoreProductRequest.php (line 28)
    Issue: images.* validation allows max 5MB but no dimension check or
           mime-type hard limit beyond 'image'.
    Fix:   Add 'mimes:jpeg,png,jpg,webp', 'dimensions:min_width=100,max_width=8000'

================================================================================
  PROFESSIONALISM — Looks amateur/unfinished in a big project
================================================================================

10. ❌ HARDCODED URLs INSTEAD OF NAMED ROUTES
    Files: resources/views/layouts/sidebar.blade.php (lines 337-350)
           resources/views/layouts/navigation.blade.php (settings link)
    Issue: "/reports" and "/settings" are href="#" (placeholder). Should use
           named routes or at least meaningful placeholders.
    Fix:   Create actual routes or remove dead links.

11. ❌ NO RESPONSE TRANSFORMER / API RESOURCE
    Files: All controllers returning JSON
    Issue: API responses are ad-hoc arrays. No standard resource/transformer.
           When model structure changes, API breaks silently.
    Fix:   Use Laravel API Resources for all JSON responses.

12. ❌ DUPLICATED VALIDATION LOGIC
    Files: StoreProductRequest.php and UpdateProductRequest.php
    Issue: ~80% of validation rules are duplicated. Single base request class
           would be cleaner.
    Fix:   Create ProductBaseRequest.php that both extend.

13. ❌ NO PAGINATION ON DATA-TABLES (SERVER-SIDE)
    Files: Most DataTable endpoints
    Issue: DataTables handle pagination via query params but endpoints could
           still be abused by requesting 100000 records.
    Fix:   Ensure all DataTable queries have a max limit enforced.

14. ❌ CACHED VIEWS STILL IN REPO
    Files: storage/framework/views/*.php (hundreds of cached views)
    Issue: Cached Blade templates should NOT be in version control. These are
           large binary-like files that clutter the repo.
    Fix:   Add storage/framework/views to .gitignore and clear the directory.

15. ❌ NO DEBUG BAR / TELESCOPE FOR DEV
    Issue: No Laravel Debugbar or Telescope installed for development debugging.
    Fix:   Install laravel/debugbar for dev environment.

16. ❌ NO FORM REQUESTS FOR MANUAL FILTER/SORT
    Issue: DataTable endpoints accept raw request params without validation.
           Someone could inject malicious sort column names.
    Fix:   Whitelist allowed sort columns in each DataTable method.

17. ❌ INLINE STYLES IN BLADE (POS MODULE)
    Files: Modules/Pos/resources/views/sells/index.blade.php
    Issue: Heavy use of inline styles (style="...") instead of classes.
           Makes maintenance and theming very difficult.
    Fix:   Move styles to CSS classes.

18. ❌ NO EVENT LISTENERS SETUP
    Files: Modules/Order/Providers/OrderServiceProvider.php
    Issue: Events like "OrderCreated", "ProductUpdated" exist in EventServiceProvider
           but no listeners are registered. These are dead code.
    Fix:   Register actual listeners or remove event definitions.

19. ❌ CONTROLLERS RETURNING DIFFERENT RESPONSE FORMATS
    Files: Multiple controllers
    Issue: Some return JSON, some return redirect()->back(), some return views.
           No consistency. Makes API consumers and frontend devs confused.
    Fix:   Standardize: API controllers always return JSON, Web controllers
           always return views/redirects.

20. ❌ NO SEEDER FOR TAX RATES
    File: Modules/Catalog/Database/Seeders/CatalogDatabaseSeeder.php
    Issue: No default tax rates seeded. When deploying, admin must manually
           create common tax rates first.
    Fix:   Add TaxRate seeder with common rates (VAT 5%, 10%, 15%, etc.).

================================================================================
  PERFORMANCE — Will slow down as data grows
================================================================================

21. ❌ NO EAGER LOADING IN SEVERAL DATATABLES
    Files: Modules/Inventory/Services/PurchaseOrderService.php
    Issue: N+1 queries possible when DataTable loads relations per row.
    Fix:   Add ->with() for all relationships used in columns.

22. ❌ NO DATABASE INDEX ON CRITICAL COLUMNS
    Files: Various migrations
    Issue: Columns used in WHERE, ORDER BY, JOIN lack indexes.
    Fix:   Add indexes on: status, created_at, product_id, variant_id, user_id.

23. ❌ FULL TABLE SCANS ON LARGE TABLES
    Files: Modules/Catalog/Services/ProductService.php
    Issue: No query optimization for large datasets (100k+ products).
           Brand/category filters are applied but concatenated queries may not
           use indexes effectively.
    Fix:   Add composite indexes for common filter combinations.

24. ❌ NO CHUNKING FOR BULK OPERATIONS
    Files: Any service that loops through large collections
    Issue: If any bulk operation (e.g., bulk price update) loads all records
           at once, memory will exhaust on 50k+ products.
    Fix:   Use chunk() or cursor() for any large dataset processing.

25. ❌ LARGE CKEDITOR UPLOADS WITHOUT QUEUE
    File: Modules/Catalog/resources/views/components/product-form.blade.php
    Issue: CKEditor images are uploaded synchronously. Large images block
           the request for seconds.
    Fix:   Queue image processing for CKEditor uploads.

================================================================================
  SECURITY — Vulnerabilities in current state
================================================================================

26. ❌ MASS ASSIGNMENT: NO GUARDED/PROTECTED IN SOME MODELS
    Files: Various Model files
    Issue: Some models rely on $fillable but others may not have proper
           protection. Missing $guarded for sensitive fields.
    Fix:   Audit all models for mass assignment protection.

27. ❌ NO SQL INJECTION PROTECTION IN RAW QUERIES
    Files: Modules/Catalog/database/migrations/2026_06_08_000003_create_products_table.php
    Issue: DB::statement('ALTER TABLE products ADD FULLTEXT...') is safe but
           any future raw queries need parameter binding.
    Fix:   Always use parameter binding for raw queries.

28. ❌ CSRF EXEMPTION NOT VISIBLE
    Issue: No VerifyCsrfToken middleware customization visible, but if any
           routes are excluded, it's not documented.
    Fix:   Document or remove any CSRF exemptions.

29. ❌ STAFF/ADMIN CAN DELETE THEMSELVES
    File: Modules/Identity/Services/UserService.php
    Issue: No check preventing a user from deleting their own account.
    Fix:   Add check: if user.id === deleting_user_id, deny.

================================================================================
  CODE QUALITY — Makes codebase hard to maintain
================================================================================

30. ❌ NO TYPE HINTS ON RETURN TYPES
    Files: Most controllers and services
    Issue: Methods lack : array, : Collection, : JsonResponse return types.
           Makes static analysis impossible.
    Fix:   Add return types to all methods.

31. ❌ MIXED LANGUAGE IN COMMENTS
    Files: resources/js/app.js, various Blade files
    Issue: Comments in Bangla (Bengali) alongside English. Inconsistent.
    Fix:   Standardize all code comments to English.

32. ❌ HARDCODED "Admin" LABEL
    File: resources/views/layouts/navigation.blade.php (line 50)
    Issue: The user role label is hardcoded as "Admin" instead of being
           dynamic based on actual user role.
    Fix:   Show actual user role from auth data.

33. ❌ NO FACTORY FOR TESTING
    Files: database/factories/UserFactory.php
    Issue: Only UserFactory exists. No factories for Product, Order, etc.
    Fix:   Create factories for all major models.

34. ❌ NO UNIT TESTS
    Files: tests/
    Issue: No feature or unit tests exist. Cannot CI/CD safely.
    Fix:   Write tests for critical flows: product CRUD, order placement.

35. ❌ NO ENVIRONMENT-SPECIFIC CONFIG
    Issue: .env.example may be out of sync with actual .env.
    Fix:   Keep .env.example updated with all required keys.

36. ❌ MODULE.json FILES INCONSISTENT
    Files: Various module.json files
    Issue: Some have "name", some have "description", format varies.
    Fix:   Standardize all module.json files.

37. ❌ MISSING API DOCUMENTATION
    Issue: No Postman collection, OpenAPI spec, or route comments.
    Fix:   Add API documentation using Scribe or similar.

38. ❌ NO ERROR/EXCEPTION HANDLING IN AJAX CALLS
    Files: Modules/Catalog/resources/views/components/product-form.blade.php
    Issue: The AJAX error handler catches errors but some other modules'
           forms may lack proper error display.
    Fix:   Audit all AJAX form submissions for error handling.

39. ❌ MIXED indentation (spaces + tabs)
    Files: Various Blade files
    Issue: Inconsistent indentation makes code hard to read.
    Fix:   Use EditorConfig (already present) and format all files.

================================================================================
  UX/UI — Looks unprofessional
================================================================================

40. ❌ NO LOADING STATES ON BUTTONS
    Files: Multiple form views
    Issue: Save buttons don't show spinner during form submission. User might
           click multiple times causing duplicate submissions.
    Fix:   Add loading spinner + disable button during AJAX requests.

41. ❌ NO CONFIRMATION ON DESTRUCTIVE ACTIONS
    Files: Various views
    Issue: Delete buttons may lack confirmation dialogs.
    Fix:   Use SweetAlert2 confirmation on all delete operations.

42. ❌ NO EMPTY STATE ILLUSTRATIONS
    Issue: DataTables show "No data available" text only. Empty states should
           have helpful illustrations and CTA buttons.
    Fix:   Add empty state component with icon and create button.

43. ❌ TOAST NOTIFICATIONS POSITION INCONSISTENT
    Issue: Some use Toastify (bottom-right), some may not use notifications.
    Fix:   Standardize on one notification system.

44. ❌ FORM VALIDATION ERRORS NOT SHOWN INLINE
    Issue: Some forms show errors via Swal popup instead of inline field errors.
    Fix:   Show validation errors next to the relevant field.

